                <p>A teacher background check is a crucial process aimed at ensuring the safety of students and maintaining a secure educational environment. This thorough investigation typically includes reviewing criminal records, employment history, and educational qualifications. Schools conduct these checks to verify a candidate's integrity and suitability for teaching roles.</p>
